extends ../layout

block content
  
  .container-fluid
    .row.row-centered
      .col-md-12.content.corpo
        .col-md-12.company_top(style="background-image: url('/images/nonprofit/header_mosaic.jpg');")
        .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
          .col-md-2.col-sm-3.col-xs-12.profile_photo
            img(src="/images/nonprofit/logo_mosaic.jpg", alt="logo mosaic")
          .col-md-10.col-sm-9.col-xs-12
            h3 Mosaic
          
          .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.not_colored
            h3.text-center.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4.col-xs-12 About us
            .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.no-gutter
              p.text-justify
                |Founded by HRH The Prince of Wales in 2007, Mosaic’s mentoring programmes create opportunities for young people growing up in our most deprived communities. 
                |Mosaic’s vision is for all young people to be supported to realise their potential.
                br
                br
                |With the help of volunteer mentors acting as role models, we aim to bridge the aspirations-attainment gap. 
                |By linking young people with inspirational role models in this way, we boost their confidence, self-efficacy and long-term employability.

              .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.break

              .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p 
                  |Website: 
                  a(href="http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk", rel="external", target="_blank") <em>http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk</em>
                  br
                  |Phone Number: <em>+44 (0)20 7566 8734</em>
                  br
                  |E-mail: 
                  a(href="mailto:mosaic@bitc.org.uk") <em>mosaic@bitc.org.uk</em>
              .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p
                  |Location: <br/>
                  em
                    |137 Shepherdess Walk
                    br
                    |London N1 7RQ
          
        .row.row-centered
          .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.colored
            .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
              h3.text-center.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.col-xs-12 Volunteer with us
              .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p.text-justify
                  |We need volunteers to help with delivery of our three schools programmes, all of which have been accredited through the Mentoring & Befriending Foundation’s Approved Provider Standard: 
                  ul.disc
                    li
                      a(href="http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk/mentor/primary-school-programme/", target="_blank", rel="external", ) Primary school mentoring programme
                    li
                      a(href="http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk/mentor/secondary-school-programme/", target="_blank", rel="external") Secondary school group mentoring programme
                    li
                      a(href="http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk/mentor/enterprise-challenge/", target="_blank", rel="external") Mosaic Enterprise Challenge
                  br

                  |If you would like to mentor on one of our programmes please register your interest via our website 
                  a(href="http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk/signup", target="_blank", rel="external") http://www.mosaicnetwork.co.uk/signup  
                  br
                  br
                  |Upon receipt of your on-line registration a member of staff will ring you to answer any questions you may have, talk through next steps and invite you to the next available training session. 
                  |Thank you for your interest. We very much look forward to hearing from you!

            .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.break  

    .row.row-centered
      .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.not_colored
        .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
